The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-23-2013 FRI
















The Glenn Beck Program - 08/23/13 





The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET, 



Glenn and the guys talk about the latest in a slew of violent crimes.
 An 88 year old WWII veteran beaten to death by 2 black men,
 and young man in Memphis killed by black youths.
 What is going on in this society, and what is Obama's connection to it all?

 Also..who does Lindsey Graham want to kill?

 And hear the tragic story on how Tokyo Rose was made out to be a traitor by the press.

 And Ben Affleck to play the Batman in the future Caped Crusader movies??
